data.description: Step into the exquisite charm of this newly constructed (as of 2021), three-bedroom, three-and-a-half-bathroom residence nestled in the heart of Emerald Isle. This gorgeous home is being sold partially furnished and is the perfect investment opportunity! As you cross the threshold, an inviting open-concept living room and kitchen await, adorned with a soaring vaulted ceiling that amplifies the sense of space and elegance. The kitchen and dining area boast modern lighting fixtures, state-of-the-art appliances, and stunning countertops, seamlessly blending functionality with aesthetic appeal. Each of the two bedrooms on this level offers its own private bathroom featuring luxurious walk-in showers, complemented by a conveniently located half bathroom in the hallway, ensuring comfort and privacy for residents and guests alike. The main floor unveils further delights with a generously sized laundry room, guest bedroom and an additional full bathroom, culminating in a spacious bedroom that adds to the home's versatile and welcoming layout.The home has newly installed gutter guards, garage shelving, HVAC cleaning and has recently had trees removed from around the home to minimize storm damage. Kayak enthusiasts will relish in convenient water access at the nearby Cedar Street Park.  Perfectly positioned within a leisurely biking or walking distance to local gems like Fish Hut, 4Js Coffee, Berts, The Trading Post, and an array of other attractions. The home is also conveniently located to the local military bases and is just 30 minutes to Camp Lejeune and a 40 minute commute to Cherry Point. This home embodies both convenience and serenity. **The following items will NOT convey at closing: Downstairs Mattress, Master Mattress, Downstairs Headboard, & Living room Couch***
